  <text>Bolts are used in the creation of <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/screws" underlined="true">Screws</style> and in the creation for various circuits and high tier batteries.</text>
  <h3>Crafting</h3>
  <text>Bolts can be created by cutting <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/rod" underlined="true">Rods</style> either manually or using a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/cutter" underlined="true">Cutter</style>. (Or alternatively cutting the head of off a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/screw" underlined="true">Screws</style> in a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/cutter" underlined="true">Cutter</style>).</text>
